    "b, Synaptic connectivity matrix for presynaptic neuron types projecting to LC or LPLC neurons.",
    "Each row is for one LC or LPLC type that we silenced in our experiments.",
    "Each column is for a presynaptic partner neuron type; columns are grouped into classes of neuron types or brain areas based on the naming conventions in the FlyWire connectome dataset 15 (see Methods for full names) and further sorted within class such that the neuron type with connections to the largest number of LC or LPLC types is the leftmost column."
